(4345, 'Erecton 75mg 4 f.c.tab', 'اريكتون 75 مجم 4 قرص', '', '12', 'Sildenafil', 'Kahira', 'Tab', 'أقراص', 'مقوي للرجال', 'Tonic for men', '75mg', 'Sildenafil is a phosphodiesterase-5 (PDE5) inhibitor that is predominantly employed for two primary indications:
